1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Honey=

4
00:01:01,470 --> 00:01:02,560
You're finally awake.

5
00:01:02,990 --> 00:01:03,830
Ying Du.

6
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,040
Ying Du.

7
00:01:07,790 --> 00:01:08,630
Ying Du.

8
00:01:09,070 --> 00:01:10,200
Let me take a look.

9
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:11,870
You're still alive.

10
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,790
Thank goodness.

11
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,590
You scared me so much.

12
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,200
I thought I'd never see you again.

13
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,120
Oh, right.

14
00:01:22,430 --> 00:01:23,280
Your wound.

15
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,240
Let me see.

16
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,070
The wound has healed.

17
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,000
That's such a relief.

18
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,190
This is

19
00:01:41,710 --> 00:01:43,120
not a dream, right?

20
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:44,190
I...

21
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:47,430
Since we've slept together,

22
00:01:49,567 --> 00:01:51,053
you should take responsibility for me.

23
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,430
I did all this

24
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:55,790
only to save you.

25
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,680
No matter how it all began,

26
00:01:58,350 --> 00:01:59,510
once it happened,

27
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,510
I belong to you now.

28
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:06,390
♪I can't tell what's real or false♪

29
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,240
Zhaoli,

30
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,280
let me be your husband

31
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:10,630
and protect you,

32
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:12,710
okay?

33
00:02:14,210 --> 00:02:16,530
♪Your gaze blooms with grace♪

34
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,400
Alright.

35
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,190
Then what should you call me?

36
00:02:19,530 --> 00:02:21,180
♪Affection fills the air♪

37
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:23,400
Well.

38
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,240
Honey.

39
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:28,800
♪To stay in this fleeting moment♪

40
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,960
Why so shy?

41
00:02:34,971 --> 00:02:36,470
It's not like this is the first time.

42
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:37,710
Just be quiet.

43
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:42,920
From now on,

44
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,030
you must never stand before me again.

45
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,560
I was wrong.

46
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:47,750
I only feared

47
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,190
you might lose your life again.

48
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,750
I'm even more afraid you'll be harmed.

49
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:58,560
What was it

50
00:02:58,749 --> 00:02:59,782
that you were wrong about?

51
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,960
Ying Du,

52
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,400
I'm sorry.

53
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:06,560
I misunderstood you.

54
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,750
You must never misunderstand me again.

55
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,200
I won't.

56
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,190
Zhaoli, promise me.

57
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:25,520
Don't leave me ever again.

58
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,800
Your Majesty, Ye Li...

59
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,520
Well, Your Majesty,

60
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,430
sorry, I didn't mean to intrude.

61
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,400
What happened to Ye Li?

62
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,240
She

63
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,910
committed suicide.

64
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,540
Your Majesty,

65
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:46,710
I'll wait outside.

66
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,360
You should rest here.

67
00:03:55,630 --> 00:03:56,520
I'll be back soon.

68
00:04:24,390 --> 00:04:26,270
Yan Che's mask and build

69
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,120
match that man in black.

70
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,510
If it wasn't Ying Du,

71
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,870
could it be Yan Che?

72
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,870
But why would he do that?

73
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,800
Ying Du has repaired the Bracelet.

74
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:52,360
It should now let me revisit the past

75
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:54,800
and uncover the truth.

76
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:00,120
This is bad! The ruler has fainted!

77
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,720
Your Majesty!

78
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:02,836
What's wrong, Your Majesty?

79
00:05:02,847 --> 00:05:03,480
Someone, hurry!

80
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,430
Help!

81
00:05:13,273 --> 00:05:14,390
(The barrier has vanished.)

82
00:05:14,653 --> 00:05:15,920
(Something happened to Ying Du.)

83
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,400
Ying Du,

84
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,040
you must hold on.

85
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,250
Your Majesty,

86
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:29,190
why would Princess Ye Li kill herself?

87
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,070
(This is)

88
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,630
(a distraction.)

89
00:05:53,630 --> 00:05:54,470
Ye Li,

90
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:56,270
you're alive.

91
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,630
You lured Ying Du away

92
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,390
to capture me.

93
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:04,240
No woman has ever entered his heart.

94
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:05,480
Only you.

95
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:07,680
You filled his mind

96
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,310
and sight,

97
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:11,310
yet you wounded him.

98
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,190
This is what you deserve.

99
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,630
This is the Flame Spring.

100
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,600
It will seep into your skin

101
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:18,950
and hurt your organs,

102
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,510
making you wish you were dead.

103
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,350
Ye Li.

104
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,750
You keep talking like that;

105
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:27,950
don't you think it sounds insincere?

106
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:30,190
Everything I've done

107
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,830
was only for the ruler's sake.

108
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,360
You are the Saintess,

109
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,390
cursed by fate.

110
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,240
He'll die because of you.

111
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,080
Ye Li,

112
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:42,160
if this comes from jealousy,

113
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,870
why not just kill me outright?

114
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,680
Why go through so much trouble
to set a trap?

115
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:50,000
You must have another reason.

116
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:52,070
No wonder the ruler favors you.

117
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,270
You

118
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,750
are simply too clever.

119
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,040
What do you mean by that?

120
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:03,120
Yan Che is not one of the Wuyue tribe.

121
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:05,000
He's been plotting against the ruler.

122
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,160
He told me to capture you

123
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:09,830
to lure the ruler out.

124
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,190
Only by killing him

125
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,480
can the ruler be safe.

126
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:15,390
Why don't you do it?

127
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,000
You think I don't want to?

128
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:20,720
But his power is too strong.

129
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,270
I couldn't harm him at all.

130
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:26,560
Now, only you
can make him drop his guard.

131
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:33,070
My wounds won't hold much longer.

132
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:36,480
(To make Zhaoli offer
her heart's blood,)

133
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,920
(this is the only way left.)

134
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,360
He found us so soon.

135
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:02,590
Zhaoli.

136
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:03,880
Zhaoli!

137
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,560
I'm sorry; I came too late.

138
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,480
I'm taking you home.

139
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,390
Let go of her hand.

140
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,950
I'll never let go of Zhaoli again.

141
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,680
Then have a try.

142
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,800
Let's see if you can leave here alive.

143
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:21,830
Whenever he uses his power,

144
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:23,950
the Frostbite Curse worsens.

145
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,920
He told me to capture you

146
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,070
to lure the ruler out.

147
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:31,560
Ying Du,

148
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,400
stop!

149
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,670
I'm not leaving with you.

150
00:08:36,390 --> 00:08:37,960
My rightful husband

151
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:41,270
is Che.

152
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,160
Zhaoli,

153
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,550
say that again.

154
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:47,990
As I said,

155
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:52,670
I'm Che's wife.

156
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:56,150
(I have to stall Yan Che.)

157
00:08:56,673 --> 00:08:57,960
(Only then will Ying Du be safe.)

158
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,680
Che,

159
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:00,990
let's go.

160
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,560
No.

161
00:09:09,210 --> 00:09:13,860
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

162
00:09:15,690 --> 00:09:20,660
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

163
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:25,400
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

164
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:28,300
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

165
00:09:28,820 --> 00:09:34,110
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

166
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:37,810
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

167
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:40,510
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

168
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:44,550
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

169
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:46,930
♪And that is enough♪

170
00:09:46,930 --> 00:09:50,720
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

171
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:53,690
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

172
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:59,810
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

173
